o-proof:
yes'>ighters and bombers are small one-person spacecraft that are carried
aboard a larger military ship. They are fast and nimble and can attack a ta=
rget
while the carrier maintains a safe distance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>F=
ighters do
not cost any money to build or maintain. They also do not have hyperdrives
&#8211; they can only travel at sub-light speeds. Thus they must be carried
onboard another ship or base.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>T=
here are
two types of fighters:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l=
0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
lang=3DEN-NZ style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso=
-bidi-font-family:
Symbol;mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'><span style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>&middot;<sp=
an
style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-languag=
e:EN-GB'>standard
fighters which attack other star fighters</span><span lang=3DEN-NZ
style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpLast style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0=
 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
lang=3DEN-NZ style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso=
-bidi-font-family:
Symbol;mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'><span style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>&middot;<sp=
an
style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-languag=
e:EN-GB'>bombers
which are better able to attack larger targets like ships and bases</span><=
span
lang=3DEN-NZ style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>Y=
ou
research fighters in the Weapons tech tree (Research screen &#8211; F7).
Bombers have other prerequisite techs, e.g. missile bombers require you to
first research missile weapons and torpedo bombers require you to first
research torpedo weapons.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

