v:shapes=3D"Picture_x0020_4"><![endif]><span
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>To build fighters you must h=
ave a
ship or base with Fighter Bay components. Select this ship or base in the
Selection Panel. Click the purple Action button &#8220;Manage Fighters and
Bombers&#8221;. This will open a set of Action buttons for building and
launching fighters and bombers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-NZ style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'>F=
ighter
Bays</span><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'> are where =
fighters
</span><span lang=3DEN-NZ style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'>are manufacture=
d,
transported and repaired. Fighter Bays are researchable components that can=
 be
built into any military ship or base. Each Fighter Bay carries up to 4
fighters.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>F=
ighters
cannot be transferred between carriers &#8211; they are permanently assigne=
d to
the carrier where they were built. If that carrier is destroyed, its fighte=
rs
are also destroyed.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><=
o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

